data.description:
Welcome Home! – a delightful Colonial-style home tailored for comfortable family living.

Floor Plan: Your family will adore the thoughtfully designed 3-bedroom, 3-full bath floor plan, ensuring both functionality and charm.

Kitchen: The spacious eat-in kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring new countertops and a generous pantry area.

Living Space: The second floor unveils a large open/cathedral ceiling living room, providing an inviting atmosphere for gatherings.

Master Bedroom: Enjoy the luxury of a spacious master bedroom with a large private bath, equipped with a heated whirlpool tub and a separate shower.

Generous Bedrooms: Two additional generously sized bedrooms offer ample closet space, meeting your family's storage needs.

Convenient Laundry: Benefit from the added convenience of a second-floor laundry room, making chores a breeze.

Storage: Never worry about storage shortages – this home is designed with abundant storage throughout.

Energy Efficiency: Experience energy efficiency with R38 walls, R52 ceilings, a high-efficiency furnace, and a 75-gallon water heater.

New Features: Enjoy the comfort of newer windows and a recently installed roof in August 2021.

This well-insulated home combines modern features with timeless charm, creating the perfect backdrop for lasting family memories.
